itemLabel: Francis Channing, 1st Baron Channing of Wellingborough

wikipedia_page.main: Francis Allston Channing, 1st Baron Channing (21 March 1841 – 20 February 1926), known as Sir Francis Channing, Bt, between 1906 and 1912, was an American-born British barrister, academic, and Liberal Party politician.
